card.title: Spy Club: Mission - Bring Back Boyd Card 3

metadata.author: Yoto
metadata.description:
Using the key card left for them by Mr. Boyd, Jane and Ollie enter Lumera Technologies and its safe to say that this place is huge! With computers and screens galore and worksheets in hand, the pair use their spy skills to problem solve, stay alert, and dodge lasers! But will they ever reunite with their friends? Will they ever save Mr. Boyd? Only you can help them complete their mission  are you up to the challenge? 

Are your kids stuck on the mission?? Head to Spy Club HQ on Yoto Space to ask for help and swap tips with other families looking to give their kids a helping hint.

PLEASE NOTE: This pack requires a Yoto Player or Yoto Mini and the physical Spy Pack to play this interactive audio game. Without them, listeners will not be able to decipher clues and take action like a true spy.
